们的猜测。</a></p><p>本周，斯威夫特被发现与电影导演肖恩·利维一起在纽约市散步，这引发了人们对她将出现在这部期待已久的续集中的猜测。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-rerecords-bad-blood-verse-for-deluxe-edition-of-1989-taylors-version-3524005">肯德里克·拉马尔 (Kendrick Lamar) 为《1989（泰勒版）》豪华版重新录制《Bad Blood》歌词</a>后，首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
开发商“讨论”“狩猎：摊牌”单人战役https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/hunt-showdown-single-player-campaign-discussed-by-developer-3523986?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=hunt-showdown-single-player-campaign-开发者讨论Imogen DonovanFri, 27 Oct 2023 14:49:32 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPCPS4PS5Xbox OneXbox Series X|S https://www.nme.com/?p=3523986 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-3.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们将继续关注游戏的这些部分”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/hunt-showdown-single-player-campaign-discussed-by-developer-3523986">开发者“讨论”的“狩猎：摊牌”单人战役</a>后首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-3.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/hunt-showdown"><em>《Hunt: Showdown》</em></a>的开发商曾考虑过在非对称多人射击游戏中引入单人战役。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/cryteks-dennis-schwarz-on-five-years-of-hunt-showdown-3402525">Crytek 的丹尼斯·施瓦茨 (Dennis Schwarz) 谈《狩猎：摊牌》五年来的情况</a></strong></li></ul><p>2020 年， <em>《狩猎：决战》</em>添加了“试炼”，这是一种单人玩家对抗环境的模式，所有技能水平的玩家都有机会在任务中改进自己的游戏风格。</p><p>提供三种类型的试炼，并且能够和平地探索劳森三角洲和斯蒂尔沃特河口地图，而不会出现任何攻击玩家的东西。 </p><figure id="attachment_3524018" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3524018" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3524018" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3524018" class="wp-caption-text"> 《狩猎：对决》图片来源：Crytek</figcaption></figure><p>最近，经验丰富的猎人约翰·维克多（John Victor）这一角色被创建来为<em>《狩猎：决战》</em>的教程进行旁白，由<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/natural-six-dungeons-and-dragons-ben-starr-hollie-bennett-3520470">道格·科克尔（Doug Cockle）</a>配音。</p><p>这些更新似乎表明游戏叙事的方式越来越复杂， <a href="https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/crytek-have-discussed-a-hunt-showdown-single-player-campaign-we-do-like-narrative" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Rock Paper Shotgun</em></a>询问开发者<em>《Hunt: Showdown》</em>是否会考虑以单人故事为中心的模式。</p><p> “Campaign-style narrative – we don&#39;t have anything that we&#39;ve announced yet,” answered Crytek general manager David Fifield.</p><p> “And it is, again, one of those things – we&#39;ve discussed what it would be like, we&#39;ve started a little bit more world-building, and doing stuff with our scripted tutorial, and having some narration and voices.” </p><figure id="attachment_3524023" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3524023" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3524023" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/hunt-showdown-single-player-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3524023" class="wp-caption-text"> &#39;Hunt: Showdown&#39; Credit: Crytek</figcaption></figure><p> He continued to mention marketing campaigns that have fleshed out the newer Hunters in <em>Hunt: Showdown</em> and “[gave] them a little more personality and backstory”.</p><p> “But as far as like, a dedicated single player campaign, or an entirely extra product that&#39;s a single player thing, we don&#39;t have anything to announce there,” clarified Fifield.</p><p> “But we do like narrative, we do like the backstories. And obviously, we&#39;re going to keep leaning into those parts of the game. That&#39;s how far we&#39;ve gotten on those types of discussions.”</p><p> Moving on, Fifield expressed his enthusiasm for the engine upgrade that will “[push] the edges of graphical fidelity” when it rolls out in 2024.</p><p> <em>Hunt: Showdown</em> will also add a new map and biome, an overhauled user interface for players to get to grips with, and the ability to inspect weapons in the middle of a match.</p><p> In other gaming news, <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/larian-studios">Larian Studios</a> has said that the <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-xbox-news-is-not-coming-from-dudes-with-33k-twitter-followers-says-larian-3523934">Xbox Series versions of <em>Baldur&#39;s Gate 3</em> are still on track to release this year</a> , and that “dudes with 33k twitter followers [are] talking shit for likes”.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/hunt-showdown-single-player-campaign-discussed-by-developer-3523986">&#39;Hunt: Showdown&#39; single-player campaign “discussed” by developer</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
